{
  "stem": "10587.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To a time when I was a little boy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just remembered when I took the break, that not only that my father was singing to us, you know, carrying us-- because he did it with every child, must have done it with me on Shabbas or high holidays.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you have to see so many stars-- I think three stars before the Shabbas would be over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so he would carry us, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember when he carried my brother Joshua around and-- and walked back and forth and sang to him, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother also used to sing, but she used to play the balalaika.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she would sing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, she would sing about [NON-ENGLISH] [CRYING] And-- I want to mention these things because-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sorry that I didn't remember before.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] that's why they will somehow may be reunited, my mother and father-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] in this hellhole.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, Auschwitz was probably the most-- one of the most terrible things that I have experienced in my life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because of the kind of beating and the kind of facilities, and you never knew when your number will be up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just felt like you're walking out with a verdict in your pocket without a date.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but I always reflected back, when my father used to tell me to not to do this and to do that and not to-- maybe he was preparing me for these kind of things.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I wanted to get out of Auschwitz very badly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the-- every time there was a transport going someplace, I would be there, you know, to try and get on the transport.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- there was a transport going some place there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was not supposed to be there because-- I don't remember the block of my-- they call it-- the barracks was a block-- the number of my barracks.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] We-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- I heard there's a transport going some place, so I immediately got in line.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You had to take everything off, all the clothes, and stand nude.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] before-- and then there was a-- a-- usually it would be Dr.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Mengele there to tell you to-- and at the same time, they would-- and that's how they weeded people out as well, not only send them on a transport, but to send them to the gas chamber, the ones that couldn't walk too well and the ones that were getting all sick.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so this was another after the first-- this was another, a constant weeding out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So-- so someone said-- pointed me out that I am from block such-and-such.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I wasn't supposed to be there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So-- so the-- the punishment was-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] you know that these barracks were built for horses.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were stables.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in the middle, in the-- in the-- they were rectangles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the middle of the floor, there was like a-- to keep the horses warm, there was like a chimney that would go on the ground floor.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you would put the fire in on one end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it would go out the chimney at the other end.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on the other side was the same thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The other side was the same-- the same arrangement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, so that-- so that there was-- the fire would-- the warm smoke would go out both ends.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] Well, I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because I was not supposed to be there, the punishment was that I get whipped.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were two-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two-- I think they were Cossacks-- prisoners-- Russian prisoners.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were-- and they stuck my head in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no fire in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was daytime.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We never had a fire there, anyways.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never remembered that there was ever a fire in these.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was only when the horses were in these stables.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- and they told me to count.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and every time I count, they were hitting me from both sides.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they were like-- it looked to me like it was like a twisted cable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I passed out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't how-- after know how many-- how long I counted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, it was very, very sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had no skin on my rear, because I had like, open wounds.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was concerned about infection and-- and how am I going to heal?",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
